Amsterdam Connection (Sing Chen, Bolo Yeung, 1977) EN - DVD/Rmvb

Plot:
Fan Mei Sheng concocts a plan to use prostitutes to smuggle drugs from Amsterdam into Hong Kong. When the gang kidnaps the same woman who ruined their friendship, Jason Pai Piao and Wong Yuen San must put aside their differences to free her. 

Overview:
Jason Pai Piao (DEATH MASK OF THE NINJA) and Wong Yuen San (TEN TIGER\&amp;#039;S OF SHAOLIN) are two young martial artists who become good friends, until a woman\&amp;#039;s affections drive them apart. Jason Pai Piao joins a gang run by Bolo Yeung (Enter the Dragon), and Wong Yuen San ends up in a rival gang of drug smugglers commanded by Fan Mei Sheng. The action begins in the streets of modern day Hong Kong, and shifts to Amsterdam when Fan Mei Sheng concocts a plan to use prostitutes for smuggling drugs back into Hong Kong. When the gang kidnaps the same woman who ruined their friendship, Jason Pai Piao and Wong Yuen San must put aside their differences to free her. Throw Hong Kong bad boy Chen Sing (Bloody Fists) into the mix and you know action, intrigue, corruption, and betrayal will follow. 

Cast:
